  "shopify.compare.title": "Why Shopify rather than another CMS?",
  "shopify.compare.intro": "For a local retailer or growing brand, the choice mostly comes down to <strong>simplicity / total cost / reliability</strong>. Here is an honest summary versus the solutions most often considered: it's a discussion aid, not an absolute truth for every context.",
